<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Install UDID App</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f5f5f7;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .container {
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 2rem;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #1d1d1f;
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .description {
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .features {
            background-color: #f5f5f7;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            margin: 1.5rem 0;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .features h2 {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: #1d1d1f;
        }

        .features ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .features li {
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            padding-left: 1.5rem;
            position: relative;
        }

        .features li::before {
            content: "âœ“";
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            color: #34c759;
        }

        .install-btn {
            background-color: #0071e3;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 500;
            display: inline-block;
            transition: background-color 0.2s;
        }

        .install-btn:hover {
            background-color: #0077ed;
        }

        .note {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            margin-top: 1rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>UDID App</h1>
        <p class="description">Install the UDID App to easily access and copy your device's UDID anytime.</p>
        
        <div class="features">
            <h2>Features</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>One-click installation</li>
                <li>Instant UDID access</li>
                <li>Easy copy functionality</li>
                <li>Home screen app access</li>
                <li>Clean, modern interface</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <a href="/profile" class="install-btn">Install UDID App</a>
        <p class="note">Compatible with iOS devices only</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 